    @FunctionalInterface
public interface SectionResolver
    The SectionResolver serves the purpose of taking the sections output by the SectionSplitter and assigning to them matching infrastructure elements returning a collection of ResolvedSections which can be handed off to the LegGraph for additional analysis.

    This will match the provided route section split/id to any and all elements sharing a common identifier. The graph solution handles the resolution of these multiple options into a single path.
